{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/前端mock/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"撸猫程序员"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b53d5e78-bbde-5534-9ddd-9648b34c5574","excerpt":"痛点 项目中前端和后端开发同步进行，前端不能及时拿到可用的接口，只能通过约定的接口定义来模拟数据，即前端 Mock。我们常用的有以下几种 mock 方式： 直接在代码里写死数据 将数据写在 json 文件里，然后将请求地址写为文件地址 使用 fiddler 等工具拦截请求并返回静态文件 使用 Express…","html":"<h2>痛点</h2>\n<p>项目中前端和后端开发同步进行，前端不能及时拿到可用的接口，只能通过约定的接口定义来模拟数据，即前端 Mock。我们常用的有以下几种 mock 方式：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>直接在代码里写死数据</li>\n<li>将数据写在 json 文件里，然后将请求地址写为文件地址</li>\n<li>使用 fiddler 等工具拦截请求并返回静态文件</li>\n<li>使用 Express 等服务器框架起一个服务，对对应的请求进行响应</li>\n<li>结合方式 4，配合 webpack 的 Proxy 可以实现在代码中不添加 mock 代码，将请求代理到 mock 服务器上。</li>\n<li>使用 Webpack+json-server 可以提供简单并且支持 REST 的 Mock 服务\n<strong>对比：</strong></li>\n<li>方式 1，2 是最简单的实现方式，但是无法模拟真实的接口情况，并且需要修改代码。</li>\n<li>方式 3：不方便维护，没有特别明显的缺点，也能返回特定的响应。</li>\n<li>方式 4：比较麻烦，但是灵活</li>\n<li>方式 5，6 两种方式其实差不多，都是另起一个服务，然后使用 webpack 进行代理。json-server 的特点是支持 REST API,可以对 JSON 文件进行 DELETE、PUT 等请求，并能对应响应。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>Webpack+json-server 实现前端 mock</h2>\n<h3>json-server:<a href=\"https://github.com/typicode/json-server\">Github 地址</a></h3>\n<p>能提供完全模拟的 REST API 并且简单易用，并且提供简单的可视化界面。\n<strong>安装</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">$ <span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> -g json-server</code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>使用：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>创建模拟数据的<code class=\"language-text\">example.json</code>文件</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"posts\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"title\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"json-server\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"author\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"typicode\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"comments\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"id\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"body\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"some comment\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"postId\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"profile\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"typicode\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>创建路由<code class=\"language-text\">routes.json</code>文件(可选，可以不创建，但是能提供更大的灵活性)</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"/api//?method=:method\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"/:method\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>\n<p>开启 mock 服务器\n使用命令：<code class=\"language-text\">json-server --watch example.json</code></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>默认打开 3000 端口，如果想改为其他端口可以添加<code class=\"language-text\">--port [portnumber]</code>参数\n如果使用路由功能，添加参数<code class=\"language-text\">--routes [routesfilename.json]</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n</li>\n<li>Enjoy it\n开启提示：\n<img src=\"http://ow67vzejn.bkt.clouddn.com/1505218490905.png\">\n访问 localhost:3000,能查看当前所有的接口和路由，并且可以快速点击使用\n<img src=\"http://ow67vzejn.bkt.clouddn.com/1505218567867.png\"></li>\n</ol>\n<h2>通过 proxy 整合 Webpack-dev-server</h2>\n<p>修改<code class=\"language-text\">webpack.config.js</code>中的 devServer 字段，增加 proxy 属性将请求代理到 Mock-server 下。也可以通过这种方式直接将本地请求代理到真实的服务器上。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\">proxy<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            '/api'<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n                target<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> 'http<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token comment\">//localhost:3000',</span>\n                secure<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span>\n            <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>然后启动 webpack-dev-server 后发起的/api 路径下的所有请求都会被代理到<code class=\"language-text\">localhost：3000/api</code>,如果/api 后面还有子路径可以使用 routes 进行匹配，详细查看 json-server 的文档。</p>\n<h2>faker.js:<a href=\"https://github.com/marak/Faker.js/\">Github 地址</a></h2>\n<p>能生成随机数据，配合 json-server 使用基本上能模拟真实的数据\n<strong>安装：</strong>\n<code class=\"language-text\">npm install faker</code>\n新建<code class=\"language-text\">example.js</code>文件：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">exports</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> faker <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"faker\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    people<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      id<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      name<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> faker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">findName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      avatar<span class=\"token operator\">:</span> faker<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>internet<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">avatar</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"前端mock","date":"September 12, 2017","description":null}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/mongoose官方API一览/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"mongoose官方API一览"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/Git工具型命令/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Git工具型命令"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"b53d5e78-bbde-5534-9ddd-9648b34c5574","previousPostId":"cd46321e-db98-50a7-9d87-6a17a2fd90b5","nextPostId":"7f0a4335-f4b1-583b-b675-4e5299c43bd4"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"]}